olds for Information Security and Privacy Liability, Regulatory Defense and Penalties, Website Media Content Liability, PCI fines, expenses, and Costs, Privacy Breach Response Services.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n','<!--Start Page Content -->\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-10\">\r\n<p>Hallmark Insurance Company is dedicated to providing competitive rates and flexible coverage options for non-standard personal auto and specialty homeowner insurance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our personal auto product is designed to provide affordable coverage for a variety of risks, including drivers without prior insurance coverage and those with a suspended license or who require an SR22 financial responsibility filing. We also accept salvage-titled vehicles and operators with a foreign or international license.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The specialty property program is designed for lower value dwellings including older, well-maintained properties. We also offer multiple renters policy options, including a liability-only renters&Atilde;&cent;&acirc;&sbquo;&not;&acirc;&bdquo;&cent; policy.*</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<i>*Coverage availabity is determined by each state.</i></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-md-2\"><img src=\"images/am-best.jpg\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"images/silver-car.jpg\" /> <!--End Page Content--></p>\r\n',NULL,'Cyber.gif','Blank.gif',NULL,NULL,NULL);
