n respond quickly to provide the solutions unique to these individual risks.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We use an efficient and superior proprietary operating system providing unprecedented service and efficiency. All business is conducted&nbsp;in an entirely paperless environment and policies are issued instantly in an electronic format providing quality service to our brokers and their customers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Distribution Channels:</strong> Hallmark Primary and Excess Casualty products are licensed to underwrite business in every state utilizing our network of&nbsp;appointed wholesale brokers. We have a strong commitment to our appointed producers and hence require all business to be submitted through these&nbsp;exclusive Wholesale Broker relationships.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:10px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 128, 128);\">If you are viewing this website with a version of Internet Explorer 8 or older, we recommend you upgrade the application <a href=\"http://windows.microsoft.com/en-us/internet-explorer/download-ie\" target=\"_blank\">(click here)</a> or use <a href=\"https://support.google.com/chrome/answer/95346?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\">Google Chrome</a>, <a href=\"http://www.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/all/\" target=\"_blank\">Firefox</a> or <a href=\"https://support.apple.com/downloads/#safari\" target=\"_blank\">Safari</a>.&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n',NULL,NULL,'<p>Hallmark Primary and Excess Casualty provides custom coverage solutions for targeted commercial and transportation risks. Our underwriters have the deep understanding of the more difficult-to-place operations and can respond quickly to provide the solutions unique to these individual risks.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We use an efficient and superior proprietary operating system providing unprecedented service and efficiency. All business is conducted&nbsp;in an entirely paperless environment and policies are issued instantly in an electronic format providing quality service to our brokers and the