LL,NULL,'<p>If there is specific documentation that is not available, contact our underwriters at 972-852-1200.</p>\r\n',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,0,0,'','','','','','','','approved',1,1,'2013-09-11 04:08:31','2013-10-23 19:27:09'),(38,'aero',9,'Policy Look-up','policy-look-up','Policy Look-up','Policy Look-up',1,0,0,'',NULL,NULL,'',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,0,0,'','','','','','','','approved',1,1,'2013-09-11 04:23:58','2013-10-12 13:31:49'),(39,'aero',9,'Claims','claims','Claim Reporting Procedures','Claim Reporting Procedures',1,0,0,'<p>Claims management services are provided to our policyholders through Aerospace Claims Management Group, Inc. Prompt notification of any loss is the first step in giving help in a tough time. When you learn of a loss or claim involving one of our policyholders, please call us immediately. Please obtain and provide us with as much detailed information as you can concerning the accident or claim and who we can contact to communicate with the policyholder or representative for the policyholder. In addition to your call, please send a written notice of loss at your earliest opportunity. Although you may use any form you desire, we appreciate receiving the information detailed on the Notice of Loss form that you can download in PDF format and complete online by <strong><a href=\"http://www.hallmarkinsco.com/pdf/Aerospace_Loss_Notice.PDF\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">clicking here</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">.</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Note you will need Adobe Reader to view and print this form. If you do not have this program, you may download it from Adobe free of charge by clicking on the link:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our contact information is shown below:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"text-info2\">\r\n<div class=\"row-fluid\"><label class=\"span3 text-info2\">Main telephone number:</label> 888.880.1289 Extension 1146</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row-fluid\"><label class=\"span3 text-info2\">Main fax number:</label> 972.852.1213</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row-fluid\"><label class=\"span3 text-info2\">Email:</label> <a href=\"mailto:aimclaims@aerospaceim.com\">aimclaims@aerospaceim.com</a> or <a href=\"mailto:wmueller@hallmarkgrp.com\">wmueller@hallmarkgrp.com</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Every effort will be made to contact the policyholder as soon as possible. If the notice is received during nonbusiness hours, we will make every effort to contact the policyholder as soon as we can. We continually monitor messages received. However, policyholders should be encouraged to do what is reasonably necessary to deal with the circumstances of any accident pending contact from us.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Claim Status and History Information</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Claim status information can be obtained by clicking on this link: <strong><a href=\"http://aero.hallselect.com/producer/claims-summaries\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">View Claims Summaries</span></a></strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Claim adjusting services with policyholders are typically provided through experienced independent aviation adjusters. In order to ensure quality service and avoid miscommunication, we request your cooperation in directing ALL claim-related inquiries directly to us and not to the adjuster working with the policyholder. Contact us at Aerospace if you need additional claim information.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Producers can now search, view and print detailed claim status and loss information on client accounts by clicking on the Claims Summaries link below. Please note that complete incurred loss and expense data is provided for CLOSED claim files only. Financial information for OPEN files is shown &quot;PENDING.&quot; Paid loss and reserve information is not provided either online or otherwise for OPEN files to protect policyholders and for proprietary management reasons. Incurred Loss totals reflects the totals of CLOSED claim files only.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>There are 3 report formats available from the Producer Claim Summary. Clicking on the Named Insured will give you a Policyholder Loss Summary listing of all claims applicable to the Named Insured under all policies. Clicking on the Policy No. will give you a Policy Loss Summary of all claims under a specified Policy Number. Clicking on the Claim Number will give you a Claim Detail Summary for a specific claim. If you need written verification of no claim history for an account not shown on the Producer Claim History, please use the Search feature at the bottom of the Producer Claim History table.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n',NULL,NULL,'<p>Claims management services are provided to our policyholders through Aerospace Claims Management Group, Inc. Prompt notification of any loss is the first step in giving help in a tough time. When you learn of a loss or claim involving one of our policyholders, please call us immediately. Please obtain and provide us with as much detailed information as you can concerning the accident or claim and who we can contact to communicate with the policyholder or representative for the policyholder. In addition to your call, please send a written notice of loss at your earliest opportunity. Although you may use any form you desire, we appreciate receiving the information detailed on the Notice of Loss form that you can download in PDF format and complete online by <strong><a href=\"http://www.hallmarkinsco.com/pdf/Aerospace_Loss_Notice.PDF\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">clicking here</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">.</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Note you will need Adobe Reader to view and print this form. If you do not have this program, you may download it from Adobe free of charge by clicking on the link:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our contact information is shown below:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"text-info2\">\r\n<div class=\"row-fluid\"><label class=\"span3 text-info2\">Main telephone number:</label> 888.880.1289 Extension 1146</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row-fluid\"><label class=\"span3 text-info2\">Main fax number:</label> 972.852.1213</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row-fluid\"><label class=\"span3 text-info2\">Email:</label> <a href=\"mailto:aimclaims@aerospaceim.com\">aimclaims@aerospaceim.com</a> or <a href=\"mailto:wmueller@hallmarkgrp.com\">wmueller@hallmarkgrp.com</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Every effort will be made to contact the policyholder as soon as possible. If the notice is received during nonbusiness hours, we will make every effort to contact the policyholder as soon as we can. We continually monitor messages received. However, policyholders should be encouraged to do what is reasonably necessary to deal with the circumstances of any accident pending contact from us.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Claim Status and History Information</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Claim status information can be obtained by clicking on this link: <strong><a href=\"http://aero.hallselect.com/producer/claims-summaries\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">View Claims Summaries</span></a></strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Claim adjusting services with policyholders are typically provided through experienced independent aviation adjusters. In order to ensure quality service and avoid miscommunication, we request your cooperation in directing ALL claim-related inquiries directly to us and not to the adjuster working with the policyholder. Contact us at Aerospace if you need additional claim information.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Producers can now search, view and print detailed claim status and loss information on client accounts by clicking on the Claims Summaries link below. Please note that complete incurred loss and expense data is provided for CLOSED claim files only. Financial information for OPEN files is shown &quot;PENDING.&quot; Paid loss and reserve information is not provided either online or otherwise for OPEN files to protect policyholders and for proprietary management reasons. Incurred Loss totals reflects the totals of CLOSED claim files only.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>There are 3 report formats available from the Producer Claim Summary. Clicking on the Named Insured will give you a Policyholder Loss Summary listing of all claims applicable to the Named Insured under all policies. Clicking on the Policy No. will give you a Policy Loss Summary of all claims under a specified Policy Number. Clicking on the Claim Number will give you a Claim Detail Summary for a specific claim. If you need written verification of no claim history for an account not shown on the Producer Claim History, please use the Search feature at the bottom of the Producer Claim History table.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,0,0,'','','','','','','','approved',1,1,'2013-09-11 04:37:57','2015-03-27 11:48:44'),(40,'aero',9,'Staff Contact List','staff-contact-list','Staff Contact List','Staff Contact List',0,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,0,0,0,0,'','','','','','','','approved',1,1,'2013-09-11 04:47:29','2013-09-11 04:47:43'),(41,'aero',9,'Carriers By State','carriers-by-state','Hallmark Carriers By State','Hallmark Carriers By State',1,0,0,'<p class=\"text-info2\">Our issuing carriers are:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"list-style-yellow\">\r\n	<li>Hallmark Insurance Company (HALL/99) for most states;</li>\r\n	<li>American Hallmark Insurance Company of Texas Inc.,(AHIC/92) for Colorado, Connecticut, Maine, Virginia&nbsp;and Washington State; and,&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Hallmark American Insurance Company (HALLAM/99)for California only.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-info2\">Insurance Carriers by State effective January 1, 2013</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(selection is based on the state location of the risk, not where the insured is located)</p>\r\n',NULL,NULL,'<p class=\"text-info2\">Our issuing carriers are:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"list-style-yellow\">\r\n	<li>Hallmark Insurance Company (HALL/99) for most states;</li>\r\n	<li>American Hallmark Insurance Company of Texas Inc.,(AHIC/92) for Colorado, Connecticut, Maine, Virginia&nbsp;and Washington State; and,&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Hallmark A